en-US.title: CHOICES - Comprehensive Reproductive Health Clinic
en-US.description: CHOICES is a comprehensive reproductive health clinic that offers high-quality, affirming healthcare services to everyone, with specialized services for the LGBTQ+ community. Their services are available to everyone, regardless of their ability to pay. They ensure a safe, welcoming clinic experience for the transgender community, recognizing and celebrating all gender identities.

address: 600 N Giant City Rd, Carbondale, IL 62902, USA
